Package com.xceptance.testbddy.core.bdd

Class Feature

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.testbddy.core.bdd.Feature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Statusable
    public class Feature
extends java.lang.Object
implements Statusable
    Represents a feature in the BDD Hierarchy.
    Therefore, this is the entry point for every test. To execute it, see the test() method.
    Author:
    ckeiner
